sentences: Simón Brand (born July 28, 1970) is a Colombian film director.
In 2006 he made his debut as film director with the film Unknown.
His next film Paraiso Travel had the highest attendance for a Colombian film in 2008 with 888,409 viewers.
He currently resides in Los Angeles, California, with his wife Claudia Bahamón, a Colombian model and TV host, along with their two children.
Two years later, he directed the music video "El Velo" for Colombian group Estados Alterados.
His second feature film Paraiso travel, released in 2008, was the highest-grossing movie in Colombia that year.
